our story
Welcome to Nautilus Bar
Discover the newest gem on Anna Maria Island and Bradenton Beach – Nautilus Bar! Whether you’re heading to or coming from a sandbar adventure, we’re your ultimate stop for an unforgettable experience. Just 10 minutes to Jewfish Key and New Pass sandbars!
We currently have a full-service bar that awaits you, perfect. We cooling off after a fun day in the sun!
Our venue boasts stunning water views and amazing company. It’s the perfect spot to relax and enjoy the beautiful surroundings.
Pull up to our docks by boat or take advantage of the ample parking at the marina. We’re conveniently located close to Bridge Street and the Bridge Street Pier.
